{"tid":330930,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【非hehe】馬德鐘其實幾正","createTime":"2017-07-21T16:21:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T16:34:04.000Z","uid":14730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"210f45ecb849f4a3f32f90f9853f28f708ec59f8","tid":330930,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T16:21:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/001952_d3c86099cfcc4fe2e4a5703d97bd83dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F001952_d3c86099cfcc4fe2e4a5703d97bd83dd.jpg&h=c7121ec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬德鐘自從轉戰國內發展，劇集一套接一套，事業一帆風順，有報道指他過去一年就賺了近半億，豬籠入水的他近期動作多多，除了做馬主、開日本餐廳、蠔吧及開製作公司，最新消息還會回無綫拍攝消防題材劇集《跳躍生命線》。拍劇之餘，生意亦愈做愈大，難怪其博士太太張筱蘭（Karen）亦不得不暫緩自己的研究工作，全力協助打理生意，幫他睇實盤數！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2vscNAe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2vscNAe&d=CKgDxfPOCJFUynQvfp2Tj9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=5df47986\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2vscNAe</a>"},{"pid":"2e7cc5e11f92b676b6024da395fd9e144883f300","tid":330930,"uid":43806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T16:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/68vzd1m9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F68vzd1m9&h=ad6ace4b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5568c488d38a8418506a63a720ab856d5d96a375","tid":330930,"uid":39274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T16:34:04.000Z","msg":"佢有次去我做個間餐廳食飯勁型 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}